    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143170/extras/420ebe85c8fc302bdf6ee5f9cf559a79.avif?t=1667714516\" width=592 height=730 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >You are the DERPED ONE! Go forth and derp!</h2><br>Derp Souls is a third person parody action rpg game. Use your trusty carrot sword as you wander through the wastelands encountering strange NPC's and angry appliances.  <br><br><strong>Fight deadly enemies like these</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[Trash Bin]</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[Portable Air Conditioner]</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[Office Chair]</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[Refrigerator]</ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\">[Oven]</ul><br>Derp Souls will be the weirdest game you play this year! (unless you've played our other game available on Steam--&gt; Nightmare Puppeteer)<br><br><strong>The game has one level + one boss fight rn. We will add new levels, enemies, items if anyone plays this haha</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2143170/extras/f19231f0b5871f9c4c8474b6aa39e4b1.avif?t=1667714516\" width=592 height=296 /></span><br><br><strong>Royalty free credits</strong><br><br>Lots of music by Ross Bugden, Aliaksei Yukhnevich, and Darren Curtis.<br><br>This game uses a lot of royalty free music and models found on Sketchfab, youtube etc- if I forgot to credit you here and you want a credit contact us at our discord and let us know thanks.",
